com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.dto.UserDto

Packages that use UserDto 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.controller
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the user management service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the information state.
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.dto
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.query
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.services
com.mhealthatlas.usermanagement.services contains all service which interact with external resources.
